Package info.kgeorgiy.ja.korolev.implementor

Class TokenCode

java.lang.Object
info.kgeorgiy.ja.korolev.implementor.TokenCode
public class TokenCode extends Object
The TokenCode class provides a way to generate a string containing code for a given Class token.

The generated code contains an implementation of all abstract methods and constructors of the given token.
